title: JKSSB Results 2017 – Jr Asst, PET & Jr Health Inspector Final Results Declared
text: Click here for Technician III (Power Development Dept) Item No. 639(06 of 2015) JKSSB Results 2016 – Jr Occupational Therapist Interview List: Jammu and Kashmir Services Selection Board (JKSSB) has released interview list for the post of Junior Occupational Therapist of Advt No. 02 of 2013 item No. 129. Selected candidates have to attend for interview from 18-05-2016 to 23-05-2016. Aspirants can check their status at below link… Click here for Jr Occupational Therapist Interview List JKSSB Results 2016 – Draftsman Final Results: Jammu and Kashmir Services Selection Board (JKSSB) has declared final results for the post of Draftsman Civil (PHE (I&FC, R&B) Department. Appeared candidates for the selection process can check their result at below link…. Click here for Draftsman Civil (R&B Department) Final Results Item No. 687 (09 of 2013 JKSSB Results 2016 – Asst Compiler, Carpenter & Other Posts Written Test Results: Jammu and Kashmir Services Selection Board (JKSSB) has released written test results for the posts of Asst Compiler, Carpenter, Jr Lab Asst, Sanitary Inspector, Technical Asst, Vocational Instructor, Telephone Operator, Veterinary Pharmacist, Village Level Worker (VLW) & Other Posts. Written test was held in the month of February.
